The '''Vlorë Wind Farm''' is a [[wind farm]] in [[Albania]]. It has 250 individual [[wind turbine]]s with a nominal output of around 2 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] each, which deliver up to 500 MW of power.<ref>[http://www.evwind.es/noticias.php?id_not=994 Wind power in Albania - Albania to Build Major Wind Farm]</ref>

